title: The Fabulous Thunderbirds - The Fabulous Thunderbirds and What'
description:
The Fabulous Thunderbirds
Their debut album, with the original lineup of Wilson, Vaughn, Buck, and Ferguson stompin' through a roadhouse set of covers and genre-worthy originals. One of the few white blues albums that works. 
What's The Word
Second album, equally powerful. Some of their best, including the off-kilter &quot;Los Fabulosos Thunderbirds&quot; and &quot;Running Shoes.&quot; The 2000 CD reissue on Benchmark adds three bonus tracks, one of them the aforementioned &quot;Los Fabulosos Thunderbirds,&quot; the other two recorded live in an Austin, TX, bar.
